sequenceDiagram
    actor Staff as Host / Admin
    participant fe@{ "type": "boundary" } as Frontend
    participant API@{ "type": "control" } as API
    participant db@{ "type": "database" } as Database
    participant ms@{ "type": "control" } as Meilisearch

    Note over Staff,ms: Host accepts/declines/completes a booking,<br/>or Admin overrides status

    Staff->>+fe: Open booking → choose new status<br/>(CONFIRMED / CANCELLED / COMPLETED)
    fe->>+API: PATCH /bookings/:id/status  { status }<br/>(host route or /admin/bookings/:id/status)
    API->>API: verifyToken + checkBanned (+ isAdmin if admin route)

    API->>API: Validate status ∈ {PENDING, CONFIRMED, CANCELLED, COMPLETED}
    alt Invalid status
        API-->>fe: 400 "Invalid status."
        fe-->>Staff: Show error
    else Valid status
        API->>API: Check role ∈ {ADMIN, HOST}
        alt Not host/admin
            API-->>fe: 403 "You're not allowed to do this action"
            fe-->>Staff: Show error
        else Authorized role
            API->>+db: booking.findUnique(id, include room)
            db-->>-API: booking or null

            alt Booking missing
                API-->>fe: 404 "Booking not found."
                fe-->>Staff: Show error
            else Booking found
                alt Role=HOST and room.hostId !== user.id
                    API-->>fe: 403 "You're not allowed to do this action"
                    fe-->>Staff: Show error
                else Ownership confirmed (or admin)
                    API->>+db: booking.update(status, include user+room)
                    db-->>-API: updated booking
                    API->>+ms: upsertBooking(toBookingDoc(updated))
                    ms-->>-API: Re-indexed
                    API-->>fe: 200 "Booking <status> successfully"
                    fe-->>-Staff: Refresh dashboard
                end
            end
        end
    end

    Note over Staff,ms: Typical transitions —<br/>PENDING → CONFIRMED (host accepts after payment)<br/>PENDING → CANCELLED (host declines)<br/>CONFIRMED → COMPLETED (after stay)<br/>Any → CANCELLED (admin intervention)
